These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: plum, apricot
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not the person eating apricot##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | apricot   | plum  |
| Sport   | surfing | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: artichoke, grapes
2 different pets are kept: snake, lizard
1. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the snake is not the person eating grapes##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | artichoke | grapes      |
| Pet    | snake  | lizard |

 #################################

 
