.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, coach
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, lizard
1. the designer is in an odd position##4
2. the designer is not the owner of the lizard##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | designer | coach |
| Pet   | hedgehog       | lizard       |

